Sec. 12.30.080.   Definitions.
In this chapter,
(1) crime involving domestic violence has the meaning given in
AS 18.66.990
;
(2) judicial officer means a person authorized to release a person pending trial, sentencing, or pending appeal;
(3) knowingly has the meaning given in
AS 11.81.900
;
(4) offense means any criminal offense;
(5) peace officer has the meaning given in
AS 11.81.900
;
(6) sexual felony has the meaning given in
AS 12.55.185
;
(7) stalking means a violation of
AS 11.41.260
or 11.41.270.
